*Privacy Policy*

Thank you for using Muslim Masbaha. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use the App.

*1. Information Collection and Use*

- *GeoLocation Information:* The App requests access to your device's location to provide accurate prayer times and Qibla direction based on your location.

- *Crash Reporting:* We utilize Firebase Crashlytics to monitor and analyze app crashes, helping us improve the stability and performance of the App. Crash reports may contain information such as device information, system logs, and crash traces.

*2. Information Sharing*

- We do not share your personal information with third parties except as necessary for the operation of the App or as required by law.

*3. User Controls*

- *Location Permissions:* You can control the App's access to your device's location through your device settings.

*4. Changes to This Policy*

- We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the updated Privacy Policy on the App.

*5. Contact Us*

- If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us .

By using the App, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy. Please review this Policy periodically for any updates or changes.
